### Get submissions for a username
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leetcode/submissions/your_leetcode_username

### Verify submission for a problem
POST http://localhost:8080/api/leetcode/verify-submission?username=your_leetcode_username&problemSlug=two-sum

### Test with empty response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leetcode/submissions/invaliduserxyz123
